column3: “I'm pretty effin' far from being a novice smoker; and my tolerance is pretty high for even the most potent strains. As I prefer really good, heady, indicas; I may have fallen in love with this strain. It gave me an immediate influx of euphoria and lasted a good while too, which is a major plus. The look of the stain that I have is top tier. Hard, dense nugs; even if not so fat. Definitely one for the grinder. The fla...”
“Soaring indica with some crazy sativa traits.”

“Excellent strain for insomnia and depression
 A little heady at first, but melts depression while guiding you into a deep sleep.”

“I'm a veteran consumer and my tolerance is pretty high for even the most high end strains; but this took me to Neptune immediately, and I stayed up there for a minute...top notch. Looking for seeds...”
“love the planets" i get all my planet flowers from Pure Life dispensary in Hollywood. FIRE!!!!!”"

“Very strong stuff. Couch lock on a scale of 1-10 is probably an 8. I tried this once at night, kept me awake for a little bit, but I've been trying at day lately. Leaves you a little sleepy after a couple hours. Smoked at 12 and still feel high at 7:30 pm. So yeah it's long lasting high for sure. Great strain, very stereotype Indica”
“Definitely a weekend strain, it takes you to space real fast! Love the aroma, littlest hit, hits hard. Overall great strain.”
“Fantastically relaxing. I feel like i'm floating around in the orbit of Neptune. One of my favorites.”
“Taste great ... smells on the loud scale 7.5... smokes great.. nice and mellow...”
